title: Derren Brown: Apocalypse (2012) 720p (Part I & II)
description:
Derren Brown: Apocalypse is a two-part special Channel 4 television series featuring the illusionist Derren Brown.

Apocalypse unleashes Brown's most audacious plan yet - to convince one person that the planet has been devastated by a catastrophic meteorite strike, that lethal infected now roam the land and he is one of a mere handful of survivors. Our 'survivor' is someone who takes life for granted, and has yet to truly value what he has. The adventure that awaits him is meticulously crafted to give him the ultimate wake-up call, and teach him valuable life-lessons.
